{"tid":278882,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[為禍三億年]連登曱甴研究所","createTime":"2017-06-10T19:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T06:35:01.000Z","uid":35774,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3bd3f0709e58957812b0c1be5482cf8efc4c0946","tid":278882,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T19:12:07.000Z","msg":"我真係好撚憎曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n噴殺蟲水又好、黐曱甴藥又好，點都係殺極都殺唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲曱甴仲會飛入屋，由渠口爬入屋，唔通真係避無可避？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家有冇乜嘢方法解決？以下歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05332db13765a458782dc1b701dc4d8d5bed554","tid":278882,"uid":15195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T19:17:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我真係好撚憎曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n噴殺蟲水又好、黐曱甴藥又好，點都係殺極都殺唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲曱甴仲會飛入屋，由渠口爬入屋，唔通真係避無可避？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家有冇乜嘢方法解決？以下歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飛同爬入屋就未試過<br />\n用過一個係街邊買既導甲曱藥兩三日清曬<br />\n原理係一隻食完帶返巢其他又食一傳十十傳一百<br />\n但過左幾個禮拜又有啲bb出返黎<br />\n再落多次藥 全軍覆沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66f19b55c0457550de85ba35cd9fc04c85daa50","tid":278882,"uid":94935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T19:18:20.000Z","msg":"我會用拖鞋拍一下 浸熱水 儲到十幾隻 落小小生粉 滾油炸 點喼汁食就最正 小小鹹小小酸"},{"pid":"fc98c8e2644b4f7eb23ce4d224fbb7d3f2b9aa3d","tid":278882,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T19:25:26.000Z","msg":"今日我打算試依啲防曱甴方法，試完上嚟報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n地台去水口位置圍圈搽一層凡士林，令坑渠內曱甴想爬出嚟時跣腳，入唔到屋<br />\nref <a href=\"http://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/safefood/risk-pest-cockroach.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fehd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fsafefood%2Frisk-pest-cockroach.html&d=q8qenZyyK4OFkbdvyKa3aE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=1327a3e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/safefood/risk-pest-cockroach.html</a><br />\n<br />\n用膠樽土製曱甴屋，生擒曱甴<br />\nref <a href=\"http://www.ehow.com/how_6245383_build-cockroach-trap.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ehow.com%2Fhow_6245383_build-cockroach-trap.html&d=q8qenZyyK4OFkbdvyKa3aE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=91df0375\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ehow.com/how_6245383_build-cockroach-trap.html</a><br />\n<br />\n將屋內放雜物嘅櫃、盒擺臭丸，用臭丸味趕走曱甴"},{"pid":"aef74343905213f53d0cb08d55e32016418a3ded","tid":278882,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T19:26:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我會用拖鞋拍一下 浸熱水 儲到十幾隻 落小小生粉 滾油炸 點喼汁食就最正 小小鹹小小酸</blockquote><br />\n食曱甴咁重口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e795549121f761b4afcd4704245cf4290490ebbb","tid":278882,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T19:32:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我真係好撚憎曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n噴殺蟲水又好、黐曱甴藥又好，點都係殺極都殺唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲曱甴仲會飛入屋，由渠口爬入屋，唔通真係避無可避？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家有冇乜嘢方法解決？以下歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飛同爬入屋就未試過<br />\n用過一個係街邊買既導甲曱藥兩三日清曬<br />\n原理係一隻食完帶返巢其他又食一傳十十傳一百<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但過左幾個禮拜又有啲bb出返黎</span><br />\n再落多次藥 全軍覆沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一粒曱甴蛋可以生十幾隻曱甴bb，但係乜藥都對曱甴蛋冇效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3cc249c997cce09267c2c62083b20790261238","tid":278882,"uid":43041,"like":0,"disli